        .row
            .medium-12.columns
                .row
                    // About
                    .medium-12.columns
                        .panel.radius
                            .row
                                .medium-6.columns
                                    h2 Learning for Everyone
                                    hr
                                    p.
                                        <strong>Become an engineer, scientist, inventor and lifelong
                                        learner today.</strong>
                                        Sunset Spark is a not-for-profit hackerspace for the
                                        immigrant community of Sunset Park. We offer free classes
                                        for kids and adults in a wide variety of science and
                                        engineering subjects like neuroscience, software
                                        engineering, and physical computing.
                                    p.
                                        <strong>21st century skills for 21st century dreams.</strong>
                                        The best way to learn is to be engaged in the lesson, so we
                                        work with our students to make sure the classes meet their
                                        needs and goals. All our classes incorporate hands-on projects,
                                        experiments, skills and knowledge that will immediately
                                        empower students of all ages to learn more on their own
                                        and use their new knowledge in the real world in creative
                                        and relevant ways.
                                    p.
                                        <strong>Learn and Grow Together.</strong>
                                        We don't have a permanent home to call our own yet. Our
                                        classes take place in borrowed spaces like schools,
                                        parks and offices around Sunset Park.  We're working
                                        toward opening a permanent location in the neighborhood
                                        soon to open up a technology workshop and offer more
                                        science and engineering classes to the community.

